guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"HIT NEGATIVO (normal) → ojos fijos durante impulso → RVO intacto → SOSPECHA CENTRAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"VHIT → videoculografia → registra sacadas encubiertas (no visibles al ojo)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"71","text":"PRUEBA DE\\NDIX-HALLPIKE","guid":"KIlvZF6UvxVdLNLiYowXag","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Evalua canal posterior ipsilateral al lado de la maniobra","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"POSITIVA en VPPB\\Ncanal posterior","guid":"hbvWY0paEa1YHwe52B16BQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Nistagmus torsional/vertical → componente hacia oido inferior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Latencia 3-10 segundos","guid":"EQDWT7-dQmMzkysHCojtsQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"Duracion <1 minuto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"FATIGA con repeticion","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"78","text":"NEGATIVA con nistagmus inmediato → central hasta descartar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"71","text":"ROLL TEST\\N(maniobra de\\NPagnini-McClure)","guid":"Ko8f-tRlxzDXu5z-Pf0xfw","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Evalua canal horizontal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"APOGEOTROPICO → cupulolitiasis → nistagmus alejandose del suelo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"GEOTROPICO → canalolitiasis → nistagmus hacia el suelo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"71","text":"PRUEBA\\NCALORICA","guid":"cR-00yZKjuoUcICB7N9Xkw","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"PRINCIPIO → conveccion de endolinfa simula rotacion → evalua CSCA horizontal por separado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Agua fria 30C / Agua caliente 44C","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"REGLA COWS → Cold Opposite / Warm Same","gu