ulo → via otolitica superior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"Utiles en neuritis vestibular / hidrops / schwannoma","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"71","text":"ROMBERG Y ROMBERG\\NSENSIBILIZADO","guid":"QWBP-HAr-kdqAesl2Gxygg","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Romberg simple → base normal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Romberg sensibilizado (tandem) → mayor sensibilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"Con espuma → elimina propioceptivo → acentua deficit vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"CAIDA IPSILATERAL a lesion periferica aguda","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"71","text":"SKEW\\NDEVIATION","guid":"0p9F-ZmUiEMBPdoZZvVV9A","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Desalineacion vertical de los ojos (desviacion ocular vertical)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Signo de lesion central (tronco / cerebelo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"Componente del triplete HINTS","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO DIAGNOSTICO\\NDEL VERTIGO AGUDO","guid":"3PukcsQ8H0IRpsbgCzczZw","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"TRIADA HINTS\\N(Head Impulse /\\NNystagmus / Test\\Nof Skew)","guid":"ccrx_kMkzxY4qrD6gT9rTw","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"HINTS BENIGNO →\\Norigen CENTRAL","guid":"vsoVuSLtI8cwqQXomUz8Cw","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"HIT negativo (RVO intacto)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"Nistagmus cambiante de direccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"124","text":"Skew deviation presente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"→ AVE posterior hasta descartar con RM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"124","text":"Sensibilidad >96% para AVE posterior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":